# Resize
Control Shift Mod4 Right :ResizeHorizontal 10
Control Shift Mod4 Left  :ResizeHorizontal -10
Control Shift Mod4 Up    :ResizeVertical -10
Control Shift Mod4 Down  :ResizeVertical 10
